        {
            "name": "Shalom ben Yosef ben Avigad Shabazi",
            "bio": "Rabbi Shalom ben Yosef ben Avigad Shabazi of the family of Mashtā (1619 – c. 1720), also Abba Sholem Shabazi or Saalem al-Shabazi (Hebrew: שלום שבזי, Arabic: سالم الشبزي‎), was a Jewish poet who lived in 17th century Yemen. He is now considered the 'Poet of Yemen'.",
